{"lemma":"مَدِينِي","slug":"مَدِينِي","root":"د.#.ن","root_slug":"د-_-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/د-_-ن","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَدِين","root":"دين","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13594"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%86%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"name","gloss":"Midian","examples":[{"text":"إِذْ تَمْشِي أُخْتُكَ فَتَقُولُ هَلْ أَدُلُّكُمْ عَلَى مَنْ يَكْفُلُهُ فَرَجَعْنَاكَ إِلَى أُمِّكَ كَيْ تَقَرَّ عَيْنُهَا وَلَا تَحْزَنَ وَقَتَلْتَ نَفْسًا فَنَجَّيْنَاكَ مِنَ الْغَمِّ وَفَتَنَّاكَ فُتُونًا فَلَبِثْتَ سِنِينَ فِي أَهْلِ مَدْيَنَ ثُمَّ جِئْتَ عَلَى قَدَرٍ يَا مُوسَى","english":"When your sister went and said, 'Shall I direct you to someone who will be responsible for him?' So We restored you to your mother that she might be content and not grieve. And you killed someone, but We saved you from retaliation and tried you with a trial. And you remained years among the people of Madyan. Then you came at the decreed time, O Moses."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13594","headword_ar":"مَدِينٌ","root":"dyn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAy^inN","text_ar":"دَايِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Repaid, requited, compensated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recompensed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckoned with."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay^in~aA lamadiynuwna","text_ar":"اَيِنَّا لَمَدِينُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xxxvii. 51], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shall we indeed be requited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckoned with?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) [See also what follows, in two places.]       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Possessed; owned; had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held, under authority:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [and hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, K:) [or] so called because abased by work. (K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayora madiyniyna","text_ar":"غَيْرَ مَدِينِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [lvi. 85], accord. to Zj, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Not held under authority:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but Fr says, I have also heard [it explained as meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not requited"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for your deeds]. (T.) [And it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay^in~aA lamadiynuwnna","text_ar":"اَيِنَّا لَمَدِينُوننَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned above] means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ay^n~A lamamoluwkuwna","text_ar":"اينّا لَمَمْلُوكُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shall we indeed be held in possession,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"under authority,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as servants of God?]. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","M","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}